headline: Is There Now an Opportunity in Intuitive Surgical After Recent 14% Pullback?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Intuitive Surgical stock right now? You are not alone. After staging a massive 104.2% climb over the past three years, and an 82.0% gain in five years, Intuitive Surgical has clearly rewarded patient investors. But recent action tells a more nuanced story. The past year has seen the stock pull back by 14.4%, with a similar drop year-to-date. Even so, there has been a subtle shift. The past seven days brought a 3.9% gain and the last month shows a 2.9% rise,...
